headline: Big Tech has a 'hook' into the White House says US Senate candidate
author: Fox News Staff
sentences: Arizona Senate candidate Blake Masters joined ‘Tucker Carlson Tonight’ to weigh in on Big Tech censorship and the ‘hook’ it has into the White House.
BLAKE MASTERS: There's an awful lot coming from the White House, and of course, Big Tech's got its hook into the White House, right?
You can't rely on Big Tech to check Big Tech, and you can't just say, well, build your own alternative, right?
Because these companies, when they get big and successful, they all succumb to the same pressures.
It's hard to know where the White House stops and where Big Tech starts.
And that's why we can't trust Big Tech to police itself, right?
